ground.schema:
Node properties:
Department {departmentNo: INTEGER, departmentName: STRING, sectionNo: INTEGER, sectionName: STRING}
Article {articleId: INTEGER, prodName: STRING, productTypeName: STRING, graphicalAppearanceNo: INTEGER, graphicalAppearanceName: STRING, colourGroupCode: INTEGER, colourGroupName: STRING, embedding: LIST}
Product {productCode: INTEGER, prodName: STRING, productTypeNo: INTEGER, productTypeName: STRING, productGroupName: STRING, garmentGroupNo: INTEGER, garmentGroupName: STRING, detailDesc: STRING, textEmbedding: LIST, text: STRING}
Customer {customerId: STRING, fn: FLOAT, active: FLOAT, clubMemberStatus: STRING, fashionNewsFrequency: STRING, age: FLOAT, postalCode: STRING}
Relationship properties:
CUSTOMERS_ALSO_LIKE {score: FLOAT}
PURCHASED {txId: INTEGER, tDat: DATE, price: FLOAT, salesChannelId: INTEGER}
The relationships:
(:Article)-[:FROM_DEPARTMENT]->(:Department)
(:Article)-[:VARIANT_OF]->(:Product)
(:Article)-[:CUSTOMERS_ALSO_LIKE]->(:Article)
(:Customer)-[:PURCHASED]->(:Article)
